title: Graham Gunderson - Magnetic Implosion Transformer
description:
This is the presentation of the Graham Gunderson - Magnetic Implosion Transformer.  As far as build information, it's worthless.  He says he'll post plans on his website but we've heard that so many times from others this field, I'm sick of it.  So I bought the video and as suspected, is worthless information as far as build goes so I'm giving it away.

Graham, when you have plans, sell the plans.  Not this.  Don't want anyone to pay for something that is crap so here it is for free
